parameters.name: ダンジョン19(静寂に潜む闇)171007_95bpm

parameters: \n<Moo>"...! Sion, be careful. I sense an abnormal magical power!"
\n<Wanzworth>"Hmph, so you're the hero? I see. You sure took your time."

\n<Louie-Chan>"Oh? You're the hero? I see. You've certainly taken your
time."

\n<Louie-Chan>"I heard you were traveling with a dragon, but could it be
that Pomeranian-looking thing? Ahaha!"

\n<Wanzworth>"I heard you were traveling with a dragon, but could it be
that Pomeranian-looking thing? Ahaha!"

\n<Luna>"Huh? Someone you know? ...Or rather, don't they look
alike?"

\n<Chelsea>"They're my younger sister and brother. Why are they here...
What's going on?"

\n<Louie-Chan>"As usual, big sis is slow on the uptake. We're not the same
as we used to be."

\n<Wanzworth>"You're as oblivious as ever, big sis. Can't you see? We're
not who we used to be."

\n<Wanzworth>"Persuasion is futile. We've come to know too much. Various
things. We can't let you pass here."

\n<Louie-Chan>"Persuasion is futile. We know too much now. Various things.
That's why we can't let you pass here."

\n<Moo>"...(What do we do? Can I really ask Sion to cut down
Chelsea's siblings...?)"

\n<Moo>"...(I can't let them do such a cruel thing. Should we run?
But escaping from beastmen is...)"

\n<Chelsea>"Nnnn! Louie-Chan, Wanzworth. I don't know what happened
after I left home, but..."

\n<Chelsea>"It's okay! Leave this to me, Sion! It's a sibling fight
after all. I'll handle it."

\n<Luna>"Are you okay, Chelsea... (But Luna feels a level of magical
power that could instantly kill her.)"
\n<Moo>"Sion... step back. I'm entrusting this to you, Chelsea."

\n<Wanzworth>"Do you think we can be defeated by a big sis who can't even
borrow a cat's paw, a failure like you?"

\n<Louie-Chan>"Do you think a big sis who can't even borrow a cat's paw, a
failure like you, can beat us?"
\n<Chelsea>"'Can't do it,' is that really such a bad thing?"

\n<Chelsea>"Because I couldn't do it, I tried hard at other things. I
found my own path. Did you walk here on your own feet?"

\n<Chelsea>"You must have been led by someone else's hand, carried
along without any effort. A little one who can't fight
without borrowing someone's hand. Really, such troublesome
twins."
MP_SET_MOVIE チェルシー立ち絵1

\n<Chelsea>"Come at me all at once! Two hands are more than enough! Big
sis will teach you the pain of a fist filled with love!"
\C[14]ED1 "The Evil Genius and the Failed Hero"
